commit.message:
Add a test for the MP-Coverage interaction

Switch the nose2cfg coverage test to pull all info into the config
file, as MP-coverage runs can't parse CLI args. Then, add a test which
runs on the nose2cfg config with the MP plugin enabled.

Testing on prior nose2 releases fails, confirming that the test is
effective.
